{"id":1731,"date":"2024-09-01T17:52:35","date_gmt":"2024-09-01T17:52:35","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1731"},"modified":"2024-09-01T17:52:35","modified_gmt":"2024-09-01T17:52:35","slug":"mission-019","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-019\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #019: Dowsing Wizard"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"class=\"text-large center\">Mission #019: Dowsing Wizard<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Tehl Town, Underground Pass &#8211; man in middle of tunnel<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Complete the main story missions up until Tehl Town<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Find 150 hidden items<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong>Gold Bottle Cap<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>A collector of junk in the Tehl Town Underground Pass wants you to find 150 hidden items across Borrius. If you succeed, he\u2019ll give you a Gold Bottle Cap.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<p>The entrance to the Underground Pass is in Tehl Town, inside the house behind the Poke Mart.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/019\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-underground-pass-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"The Underground Pass entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Underground Pass entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>About halfway along the tunnel, before it bends west, you\u2019ll see a man with a mission for you. He wants you to find 150 hidden items across Borrius.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/019\/02-pokemon-unbound-the-collector-who-wants-you-to-find-everything.jpg\" alt=\"The collector who wants you to find everything \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The collector who wants you to find everything<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Hidden items are not out in the open items as Poke Balls on the ground. Instead they are just sitting on specific tiles in the overworld with no visible marking. They can be found when pressing A in specific locations, such as on rocks, trees, or even open ground.<\/p>\n<p>For help, check our <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/items\/hidden-items\/\">list here<\/a> dedicated to curating every hidden item in the game.<\/p>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/019\/03-pokemon-unbound-the-researchers-house.jpg\" alt=\"The researcher\u2019s house \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The researcher\u2019s house<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>To make your life a lot easier when hunting down the hidden items, you can get the <strong>Dowsing Machine<\/strong> from Tehl Town.<\/p>\n<p>One of Professor Log\u2019s assistants lives in the northwest house, and if you go visit her she\u2019ll give you this key item to help you find hidden items anywhere.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/019\/04-pokemon-unbound-the-dowsing-machine.jpg\" alt=\"The Dowsing Machine \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Dowsing Machine<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<div class=\"callout-box\"><strong>Tip:<\/strong> You can refer to our <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/items\/hidden-items\/\">complete list of all hidden items<\/a> if you want a reference point to complete this mission quickly.<\/div>\n<p>For finding 150 hidden items, you\u2019ll be given a rare Gold Bottle Cap.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1732,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1731","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1731","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1732"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1731"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1731"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}